Connection Methods:
    - DriverManager with Services
    - Class.forName() with DriverManager
    - DataSource
        * JNDI
        * Java / Jakarta EE
        * CDI

JDBC Follows the Facade Pattern

PreparedStatement and ResultSet should be in different, nested try with resources blocks.

Regex
^ The Start of the string
$ The end of the string
(.*) . - any character, zero or more times (including nothing)
(.+) - matches at least one of anything
(\\d+) - A sequence of digits
(\\w+) - A sequence of letters or digits

Example Table where ENTIRE scenario needs to be tested with different/multiple test data.
